data.description: Why wait for new construction when you have the opportunity to own this highly desirable, lightly lived in Princeton II model. Offering over 2200 sqft, this true split-bedroom floor plan feature 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. This home comes with upgraded modern white cabinets, fresh paint, all new fixtures and fans, stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, large island and breakfast nook.  Tile in the living and dining areas and carpet in the bedrooms. Custom tray ceilings in the main living areas and master bedroom. The Owner's suite has a huge walk-in closet and large bathroom with dual sinks and large shower. Open concept kitchen and great room opens to the covered lanai that overlooks the lake in your backyard which is perfect for entertaining. The 3-car garage offers plenty of room for storage. Residents will enjoy the new amenity center featuring clubhouse, pool, fitness center, pickleball, basketball, tennis, kids' playground and grilling stations.
